articles.title: Hindu prayers begin inside India’s Mughal-era mosque after court order - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Worshippers are praying inside the 17th century mosque adjacent to a Hindu temple in Varanasi after the court order.
articles.content:
Hindu worshippers have begun praying inside a 17th-century mosque in the Indian city of Varanasi, hours after a court order gave them the go-ahead at the disputed site.
